-- openspec/changes/002-add-invoicing/proposal.md --
# Add invoicing

## Why
The `billing` capability does not yet exist.

-- openspec/changes/002-add-invoicing/specs/billing/spec.md --
## ADDED Requirements
### Requirement: Invoice generation
The system SHALL generate an invoice at the end of each billing period.

#### Scenario: Invoice generated on schedule
- **GIVEN** an active billing period ends
- **WHEN** the billing job runs
- **THEN** the system SHALL generate an invoice for the account

